6月17日，慈禧太后令董福祥部甘军阻击八国联军。甘军赶赴廊坊与义和团联合抗敌。在18日的[[廊坊阻击战|廊坊阻击战]]中，马福禄部三千余人到廊坊，与义和团二千余人攻打千余联军。董福祥率领的穆斯林军队击败了仓促聚集的[[八国联军|八国联军]]的西摩尔远征。中国取得了一场大胜，击毙六人，伤四十八人，迫使[[爱德华·霍巴特·西摩尔|西摩尔]]于26日付出重大伤亡后撤回天津。<ref name="Mersey Viscount 1901 177"/><ref>{{cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/historyinthreeke00paul|url-access=registration|title=History in three keys: the Boxers as event, experience, and myth|author=Paul A. Cohen|year=1997|publisher=Columbia University Press|page=[https://archive.org/details/historyinthreeke00paul/page/49 49]|isbn=0-231-10651-3}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=The Siege at Peking|first=Peter|last=Fleming|author-link=Peter Fleming (writer)|year=1990|edition=illustrated, reprint|publisher=Dorset Press|isbn=0880294620|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pHrZAAAAMAAJ|page=79|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208090914/https://books.google.com/books?id=pHrZAAAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Power1996">{{cite book|author=Desmond Power|title=Little Foreign Devil|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FQxIAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA45|date=1 January 1996|publisher=Desmond Power author|isbn=978-0-9694122-1-2|page=45}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=Ralph L. Powell|title=Rise of the Chinese Military Power|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=akXWCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA113|date=8 December 2015|publisher=Princeton University Press|isbn=978-1-4008-7884-0|page=113|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208090924/https://books.google.com/books?id=akXWCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA113|dead-url=no}}</ref>廊坊之战是穆斯林军队唯一在北京外进行的战斗。此战后，20日，董福祥军奉令回京围攻使馆，从此仅参与北京内的战斗。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wWvl9O4Gn1UC&pg=PA498|title=Some did it for civilisation, some did it for their country: a revised view of the Boxer war|author=Jane E. Elliott|year=2002|publisher=Chinese University Press|page=498|isbn=962-996-066-4|access-date=2017-03-02|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208090506/https://books.google.com/books?id=wWvl9O4Gn1UC&pg=PA498|dead-url=no}}</ref>而西摩尔军也得以免于被歼。列强也不得不承认此败是“欧洲人在亚洲人面前的丢脸”。<ref name=WZL/>

甘军与义和团列阵在使馆区的西北两面。21日，甘军攻破[[奥匈帝国|奥匈帝国]]使馆署，纵火，并在随后几日乘胜攻占[[比利时|比利时]]、[[荷兰|荷兰]]、[[意大利|意大利]]使馆和俄国道胜银行。但当天起，荣禄就承慈禧太后旨意，暗中破坏攻打使馆区的行动，并拒绝为甘军提供大炮。25日后，荣禄与董福祥的矛盾明朗化。荣禄无法节制甘军，也无力杀死董福祥，但秘密指使其他军队不全力攻打使馆区。<ref name=WZL/>

董福祥将军的战役一览：[[蔡村|蔡村]]，7月24日；[[河西务镇|河西务镇]]，25日；[[安平镇_(香河县)|安平镇]]，26日；[[码头镇_(廊坊市)|码头镇]]，27日。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=WmAuAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA393|title=China in convulsion, Volume 2|author=Arthur Henderson Smith|year=1901|publisher=F. H. Revell Co.|page=393|access-date=2017-03-05|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208090928/https://books.google.com/books?id=WmAuAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA393|dead-url=no}}</ref>

董福祥麾下的6,000穆斯林军及20,000拳民击退了一列援军，将他们驱逐到[[黄村地区|黄村]]。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_3gQWAAAAYAAJ|title=Diary of the siege of the Peking legations, June to August, 1900|author=William Meyrick Hewlett|year=1900|publisher=Pub. for the editors of the "Harrovian," by F. W. Provost|location=28, Little Queen Street, High Holborn, London, W.C.|page=[https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_3gQWAAAAYAAJ/page/n16 10]}}(Original from Harvard University)</ref>穆斯林军驻扎在天坛和先农坛外。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0Yu9Tf5leGgC&pg=PA22|title=Indiscreet Letters from Peking: Being the Notes of an Eye-witness|author=Bertram L. Simpson|year=2001|publisher=Adegi Graphics LLC|page=22|isbn=1-4021-9488-9|access-date=2017-03-07|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208090933/https://books.google.com/books?id=0Yu9Tf5leGgC&pg=PA22|dead-url=no}}</ref>

