另一穆斯林将领河州统领[[马安良|马安良]]加入甘军对外国人作战。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=eEwTAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA893|title=Encyclopædia of religion and ethics, Volume 8|author1=James Hastings|author2=John Alexander Selbie|author3=Louis Herbert Gray|year=1916|publisher=T. & T. Clark|location=EDINBURGH|page=893|isbn=9780567065094|access-date=2017-03-14|archive-date=2016-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113180520/https://books.google.com/books?id=eEwTAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA893|dead-url=no}}(Original from Harvard University)</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rezD7rvuf9YC&pg=PA850|title=E.J. Brill's first encyclopaedia of Islam 1913-1936|author1=M. Th. Houtsma|author2=A. J. Wensinck|year=1993|publisher=Stanford BRILL|page=850|isbn=90-04-09796-1|access-date=2017-03-14|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208091233/https://books.google.com/books?id=rezD7rvuf9YC&pg=PA850|dead-url=no}}</ref>

马安良将在[[民国军阀|军阀时代]]成为[[马家军|马家军]]的一名重要军阀。

未来的穆斯林将军、后来率穆斯林骑兵在[[抗日战争|抗日战争]]中与日军作战的马彪当时作为士兵在义和团拳民中对外国人作战。另一将领统领一个单独作战单位的[[马玉崑|马玉崑]]被欧洲人认为是穆斯林将领[[马如龙_(清朝)|马如龙]]之子。马玉崑在[[甲午战争|甲午战争]]和义和团运动的[[杨村之战|杨村之战]]和[[天津之战|天津之战]]的对日作战中取得一些成功。<ref>"Who's Who in China," {{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=uEoTAAAAMAAJ&pg=PA757|title=The living age ...|volume=226|author=Demetrius Boulger|year=1900|publisher=The Living Age Co. Inc.|location=|page=757|isbn=|access-date=2017-03-14|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208091236/https://books.google.com/books?id=uEoTAAAAMAAJ&pg=PA757|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_TmnfUKQTym8C|title=The Eclectic magazine: foreign literature|author=John Holmes Agnew, [[Walter_Hilliard_Bidwell|Walter Hilliard Bidwell]]|year=1900|publisher=Leavitt, Throw and Co.|page=[https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_TmnfUKQTym8C/page/n647 620]}}</ref>马玉崑在[[宋庆|宋庆]]将军统领下为副司令。<ref>{{cite ECCP|title=Sung Ch'ing|page=688}}</ref>

当义和团运动尾声八国联军[[北京之战_(1900年)|攻陷北京]]后，当年8月皇室决定逃到西安，穆斯林甘军护送他们。其中一将马福祥被皇帝嘉奖，因功被任为[[阿爾泰區域|阿尔泰]]护军使。如前所述他的兄长马福禄及四个本家已死于攻打使馆期间的战斗。<ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=90CN0vtxdY0C&pg=PA169 |title=Familiar strangers: a history of Muslims in Northwest China |author=Jonathan Neaman Lipman |year=2004 |publisher=University of Washington Press |location=Seattle |page=169 |isbn=0-295-97644-6 |access-date=2021-08-09 |archive-date=2017-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170205105000/https://books.google.com/books?id=90CN0vtxdY0C&pg=PA169 |dead-url=no }}</ref>马福祥也在马福禄麾下，在清廷逃亡期间护驾。<ref name="Garnaut">{{cite web|url=http://www.ouigour.fr/recherches_et_analyses/Garnautpage_93.pdf |title=From Yunnan to Xinjiang:Governor Yang Zengxin and his Dungan Generals |last=Garnaut |first=Anthony |publisher=Australian National University |access-date=14 July 2010 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120309054654/http://www.ouigour.fr/recherches_et_analyses/Garnautpage_93.pdf |archive-date= 9 March 2012 }}</ref>马福禄起初被葬在北京一处回族墓地，1995年由后人迁到[[临夏县|临夏县]]的阳洼山。<ref name=lvyou>"临夏旅游" (Linxia Tourism), published by Linxia Hui Autonomous Prefecture Tourist Board, 2003. 146 pages. No ISBN. Page 91</ref>

在抗日战争中，当日军要穆斯林将军时任国民政府第十七集团军总司令及[[抗日战争第八战区|第八战区]]副司令长官[[马鸿逵|马鸿逵]]叛变，做日军下属穆斯林傀儡政权的首脑时，马鸿逵通过宁夏省国民党部书记[[周百隍|周百隍]]回复日军军事参谋长[[板垣征四郎|板垣征四郎]]，指出他的很多亲戚包括伯父马福禄都在北京之战对八国联军作战时阵亡，而日军在当时占联军的大多数，所以他不会和日本人合作。<ref>{{cite journal |last=LEI |first=Wan |date=February 2010 |title=The Chinese Islamic "Goodwill Mission to the Middle East" During the Anti-Japanese War |url=https://www.academia.edu/4427135 |journal=Dîvân Di̇si̇pli̇nlerarasi Çalişmalar Dergi̇si̇ |volume=cilt 15 |issue=sayı 29 |pages=133–170 |access-date=19 June 2014 |archive-date=2014-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140318035752/http://www.academia.edu/4427135/The_Chinese_Islamic_Goodwill_Mission_to_the_Middle_East_-_Japonyaya_Karsi_Savasta_Cinli_Muslumanlarin_Orta_Dogu_iyi_Niyet_Heyeti_-_Wan_LEI |dead-url=no }}</ref>

